products_flowers.name: GORILLA GLUE
products_flowers.description:
Original Glue, also known as "Gorilla Glue," "Original Glue," "GG4," and "Gorilla Glue #4" is a potent hybrid marijuana strain that delivers heavy-handed euphoria and relaxation, leaving you feeling ‚Äúglued‚Äù to the couch.

products_flowers.name: BLUE DREAM
products_flowers.description:
Blue Dream is a sativa-dominant hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Blueberry with Haze. This strain produces a balanced high, along with effects such as cerebral stimulation and full-body relaxation.

Feelings: Creative, Uplifted, Energetic 
Flavors: Blueberry, Berry, Sweet 
Helps with: Stress, Anxiety, Depression

products_flowers.name: ZKITTLEZ
products_flowers.description:
Zkittlez, also known as "Skittles," "Skittlz," and "Island Skittles" is an indica marijuana strain bred from a mix of Grape Ape and Grapefruit that is crossed with another undisclosed strain.

Feelings: Relaxed, Sleepy, Hungry
Flavors: Grape, Grapefruit, Berry
Helps with: Anxiety, Depression, Stress

products_flowers.name: OG Kush
products_flowers.description:
OG Kush, also known as "Premium OG Kush," was first cultivated in Florida in the early ‚Äò90s when a marijuana strain from Northern California was supposedly crossed with Chemdawg, Lemon Thai and a Hindu Kush plant from Amsterdam. The result was a hybrid with a unique terpene profile that boasts a complex aroma with notes of fuel, skunk, and spice. OG often refers to ‚ÄúOriginal Gangster,‚Äù

Feelings: Euphoric, Sleepy, Hungry
Flavors: Pine, Woody, Earthy
Helps with: Stress, Anxiety, Pain

products_flowers.name: WHITE RUNTZ
products_flowers.description:
White Runtz is a potent hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Gelato and Zkittlez.

Feelings: Thingy, Euphoria, Relaxed
Flavors: Peach, Vanilla, Sweet
Helps with: Stress, Anxiety, Depression

products_flowers.name: LEMON HAZE
products_flowers.description:
Lemon Haze is a sativa marijuana strain that smells and tastes like fresh peeled lemon slices. Lemon Haze is made by crossing Lemon Skunk with Silver Haze. Its buds appear to be green and yellow with amber hairs on the trichomes, giving it the yellow tint. 

Feelings: Energetic, Talkative, Giggly
Flavors: Lemon, Citrus, Lime
Helps with: Stress, Depression, Anxiety

products_flowers.name: MANDARIN SUNSET
products_flowers.description:
Bred by Ethos Genetics, Mandarin Sunset crosses Herijuana with Orange Skunk, creating an indica with a rich, skunky, orange flavor profile. If you find Mandarin Sunset in concentrate form be sure to give it a try, as its terpene profile has won numerous cups. 

Feelings: Sleepy, Relaxed, Happy
Flavors: Orange, Citrus, Stunk
Helps with: Pain, Depression, Insomnia

products_flowers.name: BANANA HAMMOCK
products_flowers.description:
Banana Hammock, also known as "Banana Hammock R1," is an indica marijuana strain made by crossing Mandarin Sunset with Grape God.

Feelings: Relaxed, Sleepy, Happy
Flavors: Honey, Butter, Grape
Helps with: Anxiety, Stress, Insomnia

products_flowers.name: BLUE GELATO
products_flowers.description:
Blue Gelato, also known as "Blue Gelato #41," is a deliciously sweet hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing DJ Short‚Äôs old school Blueberry with GSC and Sherbert.

products_flowers.name: FUTURE ISLAND
products_flowers.description:
Future Island is an extremely potent hybrid that hits fast and with tremendous impact. She delivers an energizing and euphoric high that also has psychedelic elements and expands the senses.
